```json
{
  "id": 1,
  "username": "john_doe",
  "email": "john@example.com",
  "phone": "+91-9876543210"
}
```

### Item
```json
{
  "id": 101,
  "title": "Black Leather Wallet",
  "description": "Contains ID cards and cash",
  "category": "Wallet",
  "status": "Lost",
  "date": "2025-08-05",
  "location": "Mumbai Central Station",
  "image_url": "https://example.com/wallet.jpg",
  "posted_by": 1
}
```

---

## API Endpoints

### 1. Get All Items
- **Feature:** Get a list of all lost and found items  
- **HTTP Method:** `GET`  
- **Endpoint Path:** `/api/items`  
- **Description:** Retrieves a list of all items (both lost and found).  
- **Success Response (200 OK):**
```json
[
  {
    "id": 101,
    "title": "Black Leather Wallet",
    "category": "Wallet",
    "status": "Lost",
    "date": "2025-08-05",
    "location": "Mumbai Central Station"
  }
]
```
- **Error Response (404 Not Found):**
```json
{ "error": "No items found" }
```

---

### 2. Get Item by ID
- **Feature:** Get details of a specific item  
- **HTTP Method:** `GET`  
- **Endpoint Path:** `/api/items/{id}`  
- **Description:** Retrieves detailed information about a specific lost/found item.  
- **Success Response (200 OK):**
```json
{
  "id": 101,
  "title": "Black Leather Wallet",
  "description": "Contains ID cards and cash",
  "category": "Wallet",
  "status": "Lost",
  "date": "2025-08-05",
  "location": "Mumbai Central Station",
  "image_url": "https://example.com/wallet.jpg",
  "posted_by": 1
}
```
- **Error Response (404 Not Found):**
```json
{ "error": "Item not found" }
```

---

### 3. Post New Item
- **Feature:** Post a new lost or found item  
- **HTTP Method:** `POST`  
- **Endpoint Path:** `/api/items`  
- **Description:** Allows a user to submit a new lost/found item entry.  
- **Request Body:**
```json
{
  "title": "Black Leather Wallet",
  "description": "Contains ID cards and cash",
  "category": "Wallet",
  "status": "Lost",
  "date": "2025-08-05",
  "location": "Mumbai Central Station",
  "image_url": "https://example.com/wallet.jpg",
  "posted_by": 1
}
```
- **Success Response (201 Created):**
```json
{ "message": "Item posted successfully", "item_id": 101 }
```
- **Error Response (400 Bad Request):**
```json
{ "error": "Invalid item data" }
```

---

### 4. Update Item Status
- **Feature:** Update the status of an item (e.g., Lost â†’ Found)  
- **HTTP Method:** `PUT`  
- **Endpoint Path:** `/api/items/{id}`  
- **Description:** Changes the status of a posted item.  
- **Request Body:**
```json
{ "status": "Found" }
```
- **Success Response (200 OK):**
```json
{ "message": "Item status updated successfully" }
```
- **Error Response (404 Not Found):**
```json
{ "error": "Item not found" }
```

---

### 5. Delete an Item
- **Feature:** Remove a lost/found item post  
- **HTTP Method:** `DELETE`  
- **Endpoint Path:** `/api/items/{id}`  
- **Description:** Deletes an item post by ID.  
- **Success Response (200 OK):**
```json
{ "message": "Item deleted successfully" }
```
- **Error Response (404 Not Found):**
```json
{ "error": "Item not found" }
```
